==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Destructiveness
<hw>De*struc"tive*ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The quality of destroying or ruining.</def>
<rj><au>Prynne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Phren.)</fld> <def>The faculty supposed to impel to
the commission of acts of destruction; propensity to destroy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Destructor</ent>⟦br⟧
